snippet.title: Projekt Z: Beyond Order | Indie Horror Showcase Trailer (WW2 Zombie Coop Game)
snippet.description:
Projekt Z™: Beyond Order is coming out in Spring 2025!🔥 Battle the undead in Projekt Z: Beyond Order with robust character progression and weapon customization. Set around World War II, take on fast-paced missions as one of four survivors, each with their own unique abilities and role in Co-Op. 

⇨ Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/763310
⇨ Playstation 5: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10011418
⇨ Xbox Series S/X: https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/projekt-z-beyond-order/9MXJ58HPTXQZ
⇨ Discord: https://discord.gg/projektz
⇨ Projekt Z Twitter: https://twitter.com/ProjektZgame
⇨ Get The Newsletter: https://www.projektzgame.com

#unity3d #devlog #indiedev
